stateDiagram-v2
    %% Google Voice WebRTC Connection Lifecycle
    %% Observed from RTCPeerConnection interception

    [*] --> new : RTCPeerConnection created
    new --> have_local_offer : createOffer + setLocalDescription
    have_local_offer --> gathering : ICE candidate gathering
    gathering --> gathering : onicecandidate host, srflx, tcp
    gathering --> stable : setRemoteDescription answer
    new --> have_remote_offer : setRemoteDescription offer - incoming
    have_remote_offer --> stable : createAnswer + setLocalDescription
    stable --> connecting : ICE connectivity checks
    connecting --> connected : ICE + DTLS complete
    connected --> connected : re-INVITE / renegotiation
    connected --> closed : BYE / hangup

